productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
This Concrete works too well. It nonchalantly improves my baseball by a lot.
My co-worker Rey has one of these. He says it looks uneven.
My neighbor Elisha has one of these. She works as a fortune teller and she says it looks floppy.
My hummingbird loves to play with it.
